            "doi": "10.1038/NMETH.4432",
            "metadata": {
                "abstract": "We present a agent that combines fast mapping, error correction, and de novo assembly (MECAT; accessible at https://github.com/xiaochuanle/MECAT) for processing single-molecule sequencing (SMS) reads. MECAT's computing efficiency is superior to that of current agents, while the results MECAT produces are comparable or improved. MECAT enables reference mapping or de novo assembly of large genomes using SMS reads on a single computer.",
